officials\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3290}, {\"ngram\": \"his home\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3302}, {\"ngram\": \"correctional services offices\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3339}, {\"ngram\": \"unannounced visits\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3383}, {\"ngram\": \"authorities\", \"from\": 3387, \"to\": 3398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is not allowed to leave the Waterkloof district without permission and is banned from speaking to the media until the end of his sentence.\", \"from\": 3400, \"to\": 3541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3431, \"end\": 3441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterkloof\", \"score\": 0.9999980614739488, \"rank\": 1.938529819873362e-06, \"text\": \"Waterkloof\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterkloof\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterkloof\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"permission\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3469}, {\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3510}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3524}, {\"ngram\": \"his sentence\", \"from\": 3528, \"to\": 3540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He could be sent back to jail if he is in breach of any of his parole conditions.\", \"from\": 3542, \"to\": 3623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"jail\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3571}, {\"ngram\": \"breach\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3590}, {\"ngram\": \"his parole conditions\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africa does not use tags or bracelets on paroled offenders so Pistorius will not wear any monitoring device, Department of Corrections officials said.\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3625, \"end\": 3637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.829180924774496e-17, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 3693, \"end\": 3702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tags\", \"from\": 3651, \"to\": 3655}, {\"ngram\": \"bracelets\", \"from\": 3659, \"to\": 3668}, {\"ngram\": \"paroled offenders\", \"from\": 3672, \"to\": 3689}, {\"ngram\": \"any monitoring device\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3738}, {\"ngram\": \"Corrections\", \"from\": 3754, \"to\": 3765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he will be constantly monitored by a department official and will have to inform the official of any major changes in his life, such as if he wants to get a job or move to another house.\", \"from\": 3782, \"to\": 3972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a department official\", \"from\": 3821, \"to\": 3842}, {\"ngram\": \"the official\", \"from\": 3867, \"to\": 3879}, {\"ngram\": \"any major changes\", \"from\": 3883, \"to\": 3900}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 3904, \"to\": 3912}, {\"ngram\": \"a job\", \"from\": 3941, \"to\": 3946}, {\"ngram\": \"another house\", \"from\": 3958, \"to\": 3971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pistorius has maintained that he shot Steenkamp, a 29-year-old model and law graduate, by mistake.\", \"from\": 3974, \"to\": 4072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3974, \"end\": 3983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Steenkamp\", \"from\": 4012, \"to\": 4021}, {\"ngram\": \"a 29-year-old model\", \"from\": 4023, \"to\": 4042}, {\"ngram\": \"law graduate\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4059}, {\"ngram\": \"mistake\", \"from\": 4064, \"to\": 4071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He testified that he believed Steenkamp was a dangerous intruder hiding in his bathroom and shot through the door with his licensed 9 mm pistol in self-defense.\", \"from\": 4073, \"to\": 4233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Steenkamp\", \"from\": 4103, \"to\": 4112}, {\"ngram\": \"a dangerous intruder\", \"from\": 4117, \"to\": 4137}, {\"ngram\": \"his bathroom\", \"from\": 4148, \"to\": 4160}, {\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 4178, \"to\": 4186}, {\"ngram\": \"his licensed 9 mm pistol\", \"from\": 4192, \"to\": 4216}, {\"ngram\": \"self-defense\", \"from\": 4220, \"to\": 4232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prosecutors said he killed his girlfriend intentionally during a late-night argument.\", \"from\": 4235, \"to\": 4320, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Prosecutors\", \"from\": 4235, \"to\": 4246}, {\"ngram\": \"his girlfriend\", \"from\": 4262, \"to\": 4276}, {\"ngram\": \"a late-night argument\", \"from\": 4298, \"to\": 4319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Steenkamp's family did not oppose his parole application in November, although June Steenkamp said in a victim statement submitted to the parole board that she did not believe Pistorius had been fully rehabilitated and was still lying about the killing.\", \"from\": 4322, \"to\": 4575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4498, \"end\": 4507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Steenkamp's family\", \"from\": 4322, \"to\": 4340}, {\"ngram\": \"his parole application\", \"from\": 4356, \"to\": 4378}, {\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 4382, \"to\": 4390}, {\"ngram\": \"June Steenkamp\", \"from\": 4401, \"to\": 4415}, {\"ngram\": \"a victim statement\", \"from\": 4424, \"to\": 4442}, {\"ngram\": \"the parole board\", \"from\": 4456, \"to\": 4472}, {\"ngram\": \"the killing\", \"from\": 4563, \"to\": 4574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before the killing, Pistorius was held up as an inspiring role model after having had both of his legs amputated below the knee as a baby because of a congenital condition.\", \"from\": 4577, \"to\": 4749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4597, \"end\": 4606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the killing\", \"from\": 4584, \"to\": 4595}, {\"ngram\": \"an inspiring role model\", \"from\": 4622, \"to\": 4645}, {\"ngram\": \"his legs\", \"from\": 4671, \"to\": 4679}, {\"ngram\": \"the knee\", \"from\": 4696, \"to\": 4704}, {\"ngram\": \"a baby\", \"from\": 4708, \"to\": 4714}, {\"ngram\": \"a congenital condition\", \"from\": 4726, \"to\": 4748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He became a champion sprinter on his carbon-fiber running blades and made history by competing at the 2012 London Olympics.\", \"from\": 4750, \"to\": 4873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a champion sprinter\", \"from\": 4760, \"to\": 4779}, {\"ngram\": \"his carbon-fiber running blades\", \"from\": 4783, \"to\": 4814}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 4824, \"to\": 4831}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2012 London Olympics\", \"from\": 4848, \"to\": 4872}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But his murder trial destroyed his image.\", \"from\": 4875, \"to\": 4916, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his murder trial\", \"from\": 4879, \"to\": 4895}, {\"ngram\": \"his image\", \"from\": 4906, \"to\": 4915}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was accused of being prone to angry outbursts and acting recklessly with guns, while witnesses testified about various altercations he had with others, including an argument in which he allegedly threatened to break a man's legs.\", \"from\": 4917, \"to\": 5149, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"angry outbursts\", \"from\": 4950, \"to\": 4965}, {\"ngram\": \"guns\", \"from\": 4993, \"to\": 4997}, {\"ngram\": \"witnesses\", \"from\": 5005, \"to\": 5014}, {\"ngram\": \"various altercations\", \"from\": 5031, \"to\": 5051}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 5064, \"to\": 5070}, {\"ngram\": \"an argument\", \"from\": 5082, \"to\": 5093}, {\"ngram\": \"a man's legs\", \"from\": 5136, \"to\": 5148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pistorius was first convicted of culpable homicide - a charge comparable to manslaughter - and sentenced to five years in prison for killing Steenkamp.\", \"from\": 5151, \"to\": 5302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5151, \"end\": 5160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"culpable homicide\", \"from\": 5184, \"to\": 5201}, {\"ngram\": \"a charge\", \"from\": 5204, \"to\": 5212}, {\"ngram\": \"manslaughter\", \"from\": 5227, \"to\": 5239}, {\"ngram\": \"five years\", \"from\": 5259, \"to\": 5269}, {\"ngram\": \"prison\", \"from\": 5273, \"to\": 5279}, {\"ngram\": \"Steenkamp\", \"from\": 5292, \"to\": 5301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After appeals by prosecutors, he was ultimately found guilty of murder and had his sentence increased, although that judgment by the Supreme Court of Appeal still did not definitively rule that he knew it was Steenkamp behind the toilet door.\", \"from\": 5303, \"to\": 5545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"appeals\", \"from\": 5309, \"to\": 5316}, {\"ngram\": \"prosecutors\", \"from\": 5320, \"to\": 5331}, {\"ngram\": \"murder\", \"from\": 5367, \"to\": 5373}, {\"ngram\": \"his sentence\", \"from\": 5382, \"to\": 5394}, {\"ngram\": \"that judgment\", \"from\": 5415, \"to\": 5428}, {\"ngram\": \"the Supreme Court\", \"from\": 5432, \"to\": 5449}, {\"ngram\": \"Appeal\", \"from\": 5453, \"to\": 5459}, {\"ngram\": \"Steenkamp\", \"from\": 5512, \"to\": 5521}, {\"ngram\": \"the toilet door\", \"from\": 5529, \"to\": 5544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pistorius was first sent to prison in 2014, was released on house arrest in 2015 during an appeal and was sent back to prison in 2016.\", \"from\": 5547, \"to\": 5681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5547, \"end\": 5556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"prison\", \"from\": 5575, \"to\": 5581}, {\"ngram\": \"house arrest\", \"from\": 5607, \"to\": 5619}, {\"ngram\": \"an appeal\", \"from\": 5635, \"to\": 5644}, {\"ngram\": \"prison\", \"from\": 5666, \"to\": 5672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was initially incarcerated at the maximum security Kgosi Mampuru II Prison in Pretoria but was moved to Atteridgeville early in his sentence because it is better suited to holding disabled prisoners.\", \"from\": 5682, \"to\": 5884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5736, \"end\": 5752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria_Central_Prison\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kgosi Mampuru II\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria_Central_Prison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria_Central_Prison\"}, {\"begin\": 5742, \"end\": 5752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mampuru_II\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mampuru II\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mampuru_II\", \"dbpedia\": 